'''Rotana Mousica''' ({{Lang-ar|روتانا موسيقى}}) is a free-to-air satellite TV channel and part of the [[Rotana Group]] network. It was launched in 2003. 
It is a music channel in the Arab world showcasing the latest exclusive [[Gulf Arabic|Khaliji]], [[Egyptian Arabic|Egyptian]] and [[Arabic]] songs and rolling out the hits.

The format of Rotana Mousica also features programs covering all aspects of the [[music industry]] including news of the stars, entertainment events and concerts, and the performance of songs on the charts. 

Mousica's [[slogan]] in [[Arabic]] {{Lang|ar|كونوا على الموعد}} means "Don't miss it".

